Package net.fec.openrq.parameters

This package contains classes that handle FEC parameters.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FECParameters
    This class represents FEC parameters as defined in RFC 6330 as the Encoded FEC Object Transmission Information (OTI), which contains the Encoded Common FEC OTI and the Encoded Scheme-Specific FEC OTI.
    ParameterChecker
    This class provides methods for checking bounds and validating FEC and encoding packet parameters.
    ParameterIO
    This class provides methods to read/write FEC parameters from/to a specific Object Transmission Information (OTI), and methods to read/write encoding packet parameters from/to a FEC Payload ID, as specified in RFC 6330.
    SerializableParameters
    A serializable container for FEC parameters.

Package net.fec.openrq.parameters Description

This package contains classes that handle FEC parameters. These parameters are defined in the Encoded FEC Object Transmission Information and the FEC Payload ID, in RFC 6330.
